they’ve sacrificed Khmer kings, one hundred thousand tons of soil fifty-two thousand heritages to build their memorial room, they has recruited one hundred thousands setup special teams, transited (tracking) all foreign nations into isolation, every morning and night, we have to listen their advertising “Patrots of Cambodia” imploring Cambodian people behold our memorial room for help, our cooperation.

Regarding current political, economical system, learned Khmer youth have no choice but only following politics and economy because these two fields have the responsibilities to specify or finalize what’s will be conducted to define our life.

Before entering politics, I can make sure, she has knows very clearly all about the politics and economy because she got it everywhere in textbook, the system of politics and economy has been experiment by huge numbers of fore-parents, warlords, diplomats and politicians.

But there is one problem, politics and economy is putblematic, people implement food or water without regulation control and supervision, contamination will come out.

So, there is no way out, you can design food or water but to ensure its safety, its portioning, its medicine, its sanitation, you will need extra team responsible to groundroot monitoring steps of the product.

As I know Khmer people do it in accordance to direction of the economy system and the purpose is specifies “teture of sand, journey of rope and limits of sandpot”.
